{"tid":2044500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來29%藍絲係反國安","createTime":"2020-05-31T06:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T01:45:13.000Z","uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c0bcdd82c14b43e515a4d951702e60691f3a2236","tid":2044500,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:48:35.000Z","msg":"噚日<strong>香港民意研究所</strong>出報告<br />\n呢個先係鍾庭耀教授由HKU獨立拆出黎嘅民調機構<br />\n而自此港大唔再做民意調查<br />\n<br />\n前幾日 愛國愛黨紫荊研究院<br />\n發假新聞話委托港大做民調話56%人支持國安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gOgZcu0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgOgZcu0.png&h=983cb702&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報告pdf:<br />\n<a href=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5cfd1ba6a7117c000170d7aa/t/5ed0b43ac0854d3ba68fd8d7/1590735933444/PORI_PC_20200529_VHKr.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic1.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F5cfd1ba6a7117c000170d7aa%2Ft%2F5ed0b43ac0854d3ba68fd8d7%2F1590735933444%2FPORI_PC_20200529_VHKr.pdf&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=46b3df9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5cfd1ba6a7117c000170d7aa/t/5ed0b43ac0854d3ba68fd8d7/1590735933444/PORI_PC_20200529_VHKr.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n愛國愛黨假新聞(之後01改返內文, remove港大)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4xhJDm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4xhJDm.png&h=6dbbbce8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38e62dba077e6e667c3027fce1922834e63329e8","tid":2044500,"uid":123774,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T06:59:45.000Z","msg":"順便講吓 香港民意研究所 背景<br />\n鍾教授以前響港大時候專門負責做民意調查<br />\n亦係全港最高認受性嘅民調機構<br />\n<br />\n點解而家會分拆出嚟做呢<br />\n導火線係2007年當時特首及HKU校董董建華政治施壓<br />\n透過中間人, 要求HKU及鍾教授要求停所有對特首及政府嘅民意調查<br />\n<br />\n單野最後黃左出嚟<br />\n結果港大成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n搵埋終審法院法官做主席<br />\n結果裁定指控屬實 港大校長即時落台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2584%258F%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdCq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=a8424a06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E6%B0%91%E6%84%8F%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2</a>"},{"pid":"846132739abf13f224dc595af1b27bf3c8b99d22","tid":2044500,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"歡迎轉黃架 快啲過嚟大家庭"},{"pid":"e927e29781a858344bf6b63cbfc8163ab785be5e","tid":2044500,"uid":312332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"846132739abf13f224dc595af1b27bf3c8b99d22","tid":2044500,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"歡迎轉黃架 快啲過嚟大家庭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"唔關事<br />\n有d唔藍唔綠<br />\n或者明顯係 <span style=\"color: red;\">愛錢唔愛國，資本家</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會認同黃/泛民/共產黨/愛國/攬炒/建制<br />\n<br />\n佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">只愛搵錢，咪撚阻住佢搵錢，阻佢返工</span>"},{"pid":"9b58b7514ed93c90749631e79a1a19d2a948f891","tid":2044500,"uid":296677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e927e29781a858344bf6b63cbfc8163ab785be5e","tid":2044500,"uid":312332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"846132739abf13f224dc595af1b27bf3c8b99d22","tid":2044500,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"歡迎轉黃架 快啲過嚟大家庭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"唔關事<br />\n有d唔藍唔綠<br />\n或者明顯係 <span style=\"color: red;\">愛錢唔愛國，資本家</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地唔會認同黃/泛民/共產黨/愛國/攬炒/建制<br />\n<br />\n佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">只愛搵錢，咪撚阻住佢搵錢，阻佢返工</span>"},"c